  <h2>Cycling in the Ith-Region</h2>
  <p>The Ith-Region offers a varied network of cycle paths through the gentle hills of the Weserbergland. From leisurely tours along the river meadows to sporty challenges over the ridges.</p>

  <h3>Suggested Tours</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Ith Circuit</strong> (approx. 45 km) – Scenic ride around the Ith ridge with panoramic views</li>
    <li><strong>Village Tour</strong> (approx. 30 km) – Relaxed ride through the villages of Salzhemmendorf and Coppenbrügge</li>
    <li><strong>Spa Route</strong> (approx. 20 km) – Easy family tour to the Ith-Sole Spa and back</li>
  </ul>

